<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>秦先生当时</span><span><strong>花了276万</strong></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>买下6套别墅</strong></span></p>
